overview: Xander Corvus may be the CEO's son, but that doesn't mean mid-management maven Alison Tyler has to put up with his incompetence.  Sleazy defense lawyer Danny D and his client Tony Lucci enter the courtroom confident of winning their case.  Sean Lawless is minding his own business as the bailiff during the courts recess. The sexy Mrs. Lucci, Peta Jensen, however, is in the courtroom minding her own business masturbating.  Ashley Adams doesn't take kindly to the security guards in her office building wanting to stop and search her on her way to work.  Johnny's blonde bitch of a boss is just the worst! But Alix Lynx really crossed the line when she hijacked his delivery and tried on the lingerie Johnny had ordered for his special lady.
title: Overworked Titties 2
